            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1947-12-31T10:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-06-25T11:00:00-05:00" n="11" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d11">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>In the course of a conversation with Acting Representative in Bulgaria John E.
                    Horner, on May 10, Bulgarian Prime Minister Georgi Dimitrov commented upon
                    problems likely to arise from the implementation of the economic articles of the
                    Peace Treaty with Bulgaria. For a report on this conversation, see telegram 314,
                    May 10, from Sofia, <ref target="#pg_156">page 156</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
